ess-date=2019-07-01}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.afaqs.com/people-spotting/463_Former-Enfield-hand-Rudratej-Singh-joins-BMW-India-as-president-and-CEO|title=Former Enfield hand Rudratej Singh joins BMW India as president and CEO|date=2019-06-23|website=www.afaqs.com|language=en-US|access-date=2019-07-01}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://auto.ndtv.com/news/rudratej-singh-appointed-president-and-ceo-of-bmw-group-india-2055903|title=Rudratej Singh Appointed President And CEO Of BMW Group India - NDTV CarAndBike|website=CarAndBike|language=English|access-date=2019-07-01}}</ref> He died on 20 April 2020 at the age of 46 from cardiac arrest.<ref>[http://everythingexperiential.businessworld.in/article/Rudratej-Singh-President-CEO-of-BMW-Group-India-is-no-more/20-04-2020-189621/ Rudratej Singh, President & CEO of BMW Group India is no more]</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/india-business/bmw-india-ceo-rudratej-singh-passes-away-due-to-cardiac-arrest/articleshow/75251335.cms|title=Rudratej Singh: BMW India CEO Rudratej Singh passes away due to cardiac arrest {{!}} India Business News - Times of India|last=Apr 20|first=PTI {{!}} Updated:|last2=2020|website=The Times of India|language=en|access-date=2020-04-23|last3=Ist|first3=23:33}}</ref>\n\n== Other activities ==\nSingh represented India as an amateur golfer and won 18 titles globally.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://overdrive.in/news-cars-auto/rudratej-singh-appointed-as-new-president-of-royal-enfield/|title=Rudratej Singh appointed as new president of Royal Enfield|website=Overdrive|language=en|access-date=2019-07-08}}</ref> He was also a board member of the Women\u2019s Golf Association of India (WGAI),<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://issuu.com/golfdigestindia/docs/gd_02_2018/34|title=Golf Digest India - February 2018|website=Issuu|language=en|access-date=2019-07-08}}</ref> and helped run a charity for underprivileged (girl) children.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cmocouncil.org/profiles/7486|title=Members - CMO Council\u2122|website=www.cmocouncil.org|access-date=2019-07-08}}</ref> He spoke regularly at various business and brand forums across the world.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.autocarindia.com/bike-news/rudratej-singh-is-royal-enfield8217s-new-president-392882|title=Rudratej Singh is Royal Enfield's new President|website=Autocar India|language=en|access-date=2019-07-08}}</ref>\n\n==Awards and honors==\n* 2012 - Marketer of the Year by the World CMO Council - Asia<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiainfoline.com/article/news-top-story/royal-enfield-appoints-rudratej-singh-as-president-115011900010_1.html|title=Royal Enfield appoints Rudratej Singh as President|website=www.indiainfoline.com|language=en|access-date=2019-07-08}}</ref>\n*2007 - Hindustan Unilever Directors Award<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/hul-allcargo-top-honchos-win-the-last-leg-of-et-golf/articleshow/5635162.cms?from=mdr|title=HUL, Allcargo top honchos win the last leg of ET golf|date=2010-03-03|work=The Economic Times|access-date=2019-07-08}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Singh, Rudratej}}\n[[Category:1970s births]]\n[[Category:2020 deaths]]\n[[Category:BMW people]]\n[[Category:Institute of Management Technology, Ghaziabad alumni]]\n[[Category:University of Delhi alumni]]\n[[Category:Place of death missing]]\n[[Category:Place of birth missing]]\n[[Category:Harvard Business School Advanced Management Program attendees]]\n", "name_user": "Bagumba", "label": "safe", "comment": "MOS:OVERLINK", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rudratej_Singh"}
